Name: djangocms-youtube-lazyload
Version: 1.0.1
Summary: DjangoCMS YouTube video embed plugin with minimal impact
Home-page: https://github.com/jeroenpeters1986/djangocms-youtube-lazyload
Author: Jeroen Peters
